ellipse 1.54,0.18 0.045,0.030 stroke #1a4a10 0.7
ellipse 1.48,0.42 0.040,0.025 fill #3a7a28 0.85
ellipse 1.48,0.42 0.040,0.025 stroke #1a4a10 0.7
